:{{A|VO side2 baishi qingque 115.ogg}} '''Qingque:''' In my opinion, you enjoy playing the role of a joker, spouting off outrageous opinions just to seem objective and indifferent whenever you feel like it.
:{{A|VO side2 baishi scott 243.ogg}} '''Skott:''' E&mdash;Enough! Shut up! What do you know about me!? Don't act like you know everything!
:{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 304.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Wow, you really got under Skott's skin with just a few words.
:{{A|VO side2 baishi scott 244.ogg}} '''Skott:''' Well, you almost got me. I'm here to... have a duel, not to debate with you.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Skott got hit where it hurts.
::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 305.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Yeah, Skott couldn't come up with a comeback.
::Diviners are indeed not to be trifled with.
::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 306.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' I'd better not mess with the Divination Commission anymore.
::Is this really the same harmless little sparrow we all know? More like one ferocious eagle.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Diviners are indeed not to be trifled with.
::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 306.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' I'd better not mess with the Divination Commission anymore.
::Is this really the same harmless little sparrow we all know? More like one ferocious eagle.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is this really the same harmless little sparrow we all know? More like one ferocious eagle.
:{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 307.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' I guess not! Eagle sounds about right.
:{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 308.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' That's the spirit! Strike while the iron is hot!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Well, I know a thing or two about convincing Skott...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Leave it to me! I'm an expert negotiator!
{{Dialogue End}}

